text: (chaur changcha) nowpel del puok kmean chomnue ban bangkeun pheap kraeutakratm nowknong chetd robsa puokke del chea pheap kraeutakratm nei samy lngongkhlaw( moun sasanea ai sla m mokadl)noh a l laoh ban banhchouh pheap nungonr towleu anakneasar robsa trong ning towleu banda anak del mean chomnue . haey trong ban dak b nhnh te towleu puokke nouv peaky kaotakhlach haey puokke chea anak del sakdesam bamphot nung vea ning chea anak krobkrong vea . haey a l laoh doeng bamphot nouv real avei teangoasa
